Description ROBO GEISHA- 24x36” POSTER ART PRINT

By Robert "Kung Fu Bob" O'Brien

May, 2013

This art was created for the DVD cover of the German release of the film by Midori Impuls.

This artwork has been professionally reproduced as vibrant 24x36" prints on semi-gloss, heavy-duty poster paper. Shipping All prints will be signed and shipped rolled, in a super heavy-duty, protective cardboard tube. Shipping (and packing) within USA is $6.50 for Priority Mail International Shipping (and packing) to outside of the USA, $6.50 for 1st Class Air Mail. $0.50 shipping fee per each additional print to be shipped. If you purchase 5 or more prints you get FREE SHIPPING.
